Test Scenarios:

Addition:
Test case 1: 2 + 2 = 4
Test case 2: 5 + 3 = 8
Test case 3: 10 + 0 = 10
Subtraction:
Test case 1: 5 - 2 = 3
Test case 2: 10 - 5 = 5
Test case 3: 0 - 0 = 0
Multiplication:
Test case 1: 2 * 3 = 6
Test case 2: 4 * 5 = 20
Test case 3: 0 * 5 = 0
Division:
Test case 1: 10 / 2 = 5
Test case 2: 15 / 3 = 5
Test case 3: 0 / 5 = Error (division by zero)
Error Handling:
Test case 1: Enter invalid input (e.g., "abc" instead of a number)
Test case 2: Divide by zero
